							<div class="tab-pane active" id="releases">					
								<p><a href=/News/Press/docs/2013/sgsm15322.doc.htm>Secretary-General, at Millennium Goals Event, Says Sustainable Development &#8216;Must Be Based on Commitment to Eradicating Poverty&#8217;</a></p>
